songs.title: Safe
songs.lyrics:

Shoot a motherfucker in the face (In the face)
She gon' give me top inside the Wraith (In the Wraith)
I keep all my rackades in the safe (Cha-ching, cha-ching)
Combination, put it in the safe

I can't sleep until them pussies in the grave

My homies just took your bitch, my nigga, that's your fault

Don't gotta say much, load it up and I'm lettin' my gun talk
